@startuml
title 온라인 서점 - 모듈 uses View
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

package "catalog" as catalog {
  [Catalog API] as catalogApi
  [Catalog Repository] as catalogRepo
}

package "order" as order {
  [Order Application] as orderApp
  [Order Domain] as orderDomain
  [Payment Port] as paymentPort
}

package "payment" as payment {
  [Payment Adapter] as paymentAdapter
}

package "shared" as shared {
  [Money] as money
}

catalogApi ..> catalogRepo : uses
catalogRepo ..> money : uses
orderApp ..> orderDomain : uses
orderApp ..> catalogApi : uses
orderApp ..> paymentPort : uses
paymentAdapter ..> paymentPort : implements
orderDomain ..> money : uses

legend bottom
  점선 화살표 A ..> B: A의 올바른 구현이 B에 의존한다.
  이 View는 런타임 호출 순서나 배포 위치를 표현하지 않는다.
endlegend
@enduml
